text: Gheorghe Dogărescu (15 May 1960 − 19 August 2020) was a Romanian handball player. He won a bronze medal at the 1984 Olympics. He was born in Viziru, Romania.Gheorghe Dogărescu. sports-reference.com Dogărescu died on 19 August 2020, aged 60.A murit fostul handbalist Gheorghe Dogărescu, medaliat cu bronz la Olimpiada din 1984 ==References== Category:1960 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Romania
